在2013年6月9日<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/books/best-sellers/mass-market-paperback/2013/06/09 |title=Paperback Mass-Market Fiction |publisher=''The New York Times'' |date=2013-06-09 |accessdate=2013-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190729113123/https://www.nytimes.com/books/best-sellers/mass-market-paperback/2013/06/09 |archive-date=2019-07-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、8月11日<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.nytimes.com/books/best-sellers/mass-market-paperback/2013/08/11 | work=''The New York Times'' | title=Paperback Mass-Market Fiction | date=2013-08-11 | accessdate=2013-11-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190729105252/https://www.nytimes.com/books/best-sellers/mass-market-paperback/2013/08/11 | archive-date=2019-07-29 | dead-url=no }}</ref>、9月1日<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.nytimes.com/books/best-sellers/mass-market-paperback/2013/09/01 | work=''The New York Times'' | title=Paperback Mass-Market Fiction | date=2013-09-01 | accessdate=2013-11-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190729105250/https://www.nytimes.com/books/best-sellers/mass-market-paperback/2013/09/01 | archive-date=2019-07-29 | dead-url=no }}</ref>、9月8日<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.nytimes.com/books/best-sellers/mass-market-paperback/2013/09/08 | work=''The New York Times'' | title=Paperback Mass-Market Fiction | date=2013-09-08 | accessdate=2013-11-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190729110114/https://www.nytimes.com/books/best-sellers/mass-market-paperback/2013/09/08 | archive-date=2019-07-29 | dead-url=no }}</ref>、10月27日<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.nytimes.com/books/best-sellers/mass-market-paperback/2013/10/27 | work=''The New York Times'' | title=Paperback Mass-Market Fiction | date=2013-10-27 | accessdate=2013-11-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190729104519/https://www.nytimes.com/books/best-sellers/mass-market-paperback/2013/10/27 | archive-date=2019-07-29 | dead-url=no }}</ref>、11月3日<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/books/best-sellers/mass-market-paperback/2013/11/03 |title=Paperback Mass-Market Fiction |publisher=''The New York Times'' |date=2013-11-03 |accessdate=2013-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190729104516/https://www.nytimes.com/books/best-sellers/mass-market-paperback/2013/11/03 |archive-date=2019-07-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>、11月10日<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.nytimes.com/books/best-sellers/mass-market-paperback/2013/11/10 | work=''The New York Times'' | title=Paperback Mass-Market Fiction | date=2013-11-10 | accessdate=2013-11-11 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190729104522/https://www.nytimes.com/books/best-sellers/mass-market-paperback/2013/11/10 | archive-date=2019-07-29 | dead-url=no }}</ref>和11月24日<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.nytimes.com/books/best-sellers/2013/11/24/mass-market-paperback/ | work=''The New York Times'' | title=Paperback Mass-Market Fiction | date=2013-11-24 | accessdate=2013-11-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170127223403/http://www.nytimes.com/books/best-sellers/2013/11/24/mass-market-paperback/ | archive-date=2017-01-27 | dead-url=no }}</ref>，《戰爭遊戲》登上《紐約時報》在週末列出的「最暢銷的平裝大眾小說」榜首。

=== 負面評價 ===

該小說的暴力元素遭到了部分人士的批評。美國科幻女作家{{link-en|伊萊恩·瑞芙|Elaine Radford}}認為卡德刻意用安德這個角色來隱喻[[阿道夫·希特勒|阿道夫·希特勒]]，並批評書中的暴力情節，特別是和主角安德有關的部分<ref name="Elaine-2">{{cite web|url=http://peachfront.diaryland.com/enderhitlte.html|title=Ender and Hitler: Sympathy for the Superman (20 Years Later)|last=Radford|first=Elaine|date=2007-03-26|publisher=Peachfront Speaks|accessdate=2009-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081224074736/http://peachfront.diaryland.com/enderhitlte.html|archive-date=2008-12-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。不過，美國作家{{link-en|約翰·凱賽爾|John Kessel}}在他的文章中反駁了瑞芙的批評，寫道「安德解決了他的敵人，而且道德觀依舊純潔無瑕。他什麼錯都沒有」<ref name="Kessel">{{cite web |url=http://www4.ncsu.edu/~tenshi/Killer_000.htm |title=Creating the Innocent Killer:  Ender's Game, Intention, and Morality |last=Kessel |first=John |year=2004 |publisher=Science Fiction Foundation |accessdate=2009-01-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20081227053817/http://www4.ncsu.edu/~tenshi/Killer_000.htm |archivedate=2008-12-27 }}</ref>。2014年，作家諾亞·柏拉斯基（{{lang|en|Noah Berlatsky}}）在刊登於雜誌《[[大西洋_(雜誌)|大西洋]]》上的一篇文章中表示，《戰爭遊戲》根本是在聲明「西方勢力拓展和種族清洗」是正當的<ref name="Atlantic_SF_imperial">{{cite web |url=https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2014/04/why-sci-fi-keeps-imagining-the-enslavement-of-white-people/361173/ |title=Why Sci-Fi Keeps Imagining the Subjugation of White People |website=''The Atlantic'' |date=2014-04-25 |first=Noah |last=Berlatsky |accessdate=2015-03-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150316174827/http://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2014/04/why-sci-fi-keeps-imagining-the-enslavement-of-white-people/361173/ |archive-date=2015-03-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。除了暴力元素外，卡德也表示，書中對資優兒童的描繪被一些家長批評「不真實」，而簡單易讀的內容也被一些支持深奧晦澀文學的文壇專業人士瞧不起<ref>{{Harvnb|歐森·史考特·卡德|2013|p=407-409}}</ref>。

=== 其他 ===

專門教育[[美国海军陆战队|美国海军陆战队]]成員的[[海軍陸戰隊大學|海軍陸戰隊大學]]一開始將《戰爭遊戲》列入較低位階學員的推薦閱讀書單中，而後來也將其推薦給{{link-en|候補軍官|Officer candidate}}和{{link-en|海軍學校學員|Midshipman}}閱讀<ref>{{cite web | title = USMC Professional Reading Program (website) | work = Reading List by Grade | publisher = [[海軍陸戰隊大學|Marine Corps University]] | date = 2014-12-13 | url = http://guides.grc.usmcu.edu/content.php?pid=408059&sid=4909977 | format = Website | accessdate = 2014-12-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141214004329/http://guides.grc.usmcu.edu/content.php?pid=408059&sid=4909977 | archive-date = 2014-12-14 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。《戰爭遊戲》也被海軍陸戰隊的約翰·F·史密特上尉（{{lang|en|Captain John F. Schmitt}}）採用，當作任教科目的教材<ref name="P414">{{Harvnb|歐森·史考特·卡德|2013|p=414}}</ref><ref name ="USMCEnders3">{{cite web | title = Ender's Game Discussion Guide | work = USMC Professional Reading Program | publisher = Marine Corps University | date = 2009-09-25 | url = http://www.mcu.usmc.mil/lejeune_leadership/LLI%20Documnets/Enders'%20Game%203.pdf | format = PDF | accessdate = 2010-09-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110124133745/http://www.mcu.usmc.mil/lejeune_leadership/LLI%20Documnets/Enders'%20Game%203.pdf | archive-date = 2011-01-24 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>。除此之外，{{link-en|勒瓊營海軍陸戰隊基地|Marine Corps Base Camp Lejeune|勒瓊營}}也對《戰爭遊戲》青睞有加，認為其「在教學方式、領導力和道德等方面都給我們上了一課」，並表示，「《戰爭遊戲》一直以來都是推薦書單上的常客」<ref name="USMCEnders3"/>。

[[北卡羅萊納州|北卡羅萊納州]][[阿帕拉契山|阿帕拉契山]]州立大學沃特加學院的科際整合課程也採用了《戰爭遊戲》為教材，當作「個人解決問題和激發創意」的參考書<ref name="P414"/>。除了成人圈外，卡德在後記中表示，《戰爭遊戲》尤其受到兒童們的喜愛，成功引起共鳴。卡德認為這種現象的原因，是該小說肯定了兒童的特質。他提到，[[猶他州|猶他州]][[普若佛|普若佛市]]法瑞爾初中圖書館的館員曾告訴他，「《戰爭遊戲》是我們失竊最嚴重的一本書」。<ref>{{Harvnb|歐森·史考特·卡德|2013|p=409}}</ref>

== 修訂版 ==

1991年，卡德對《戰爭遊戲》進行了小幅修訂，改動的部分包含更正錯誤、修改矛盾之處和修飾文字<ref>{{Harvnb|歐森·史考特·卡德|2013|p=399}}</ref>。另外，在修訂版中，卡德也更新了一些涉及現實的政治內容，以便更準確地反映時代<ref name="The Guardian"/>；如[[蘇聯|蘇聯]]的解體。在後續作品《{{link-en|安德的流亡|Ender in Exile}}》（2008年）的後記中，卡德表示，他更改了《戰爭遊戲》第15章的許多細節，好為後續作品鋪路。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://us.macmillan.com/enderinexile|title=Ender in Exile Audio edition|work=Macmillan Audio|date=November 2008|access-date=2019-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160401041300/http://us.macmillan.com/enderinexile|archive-date=2016-04-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

== 後續作品 ==

《戰爭遊戲》出版後，卡德接著發表了多部續集：在《戰爭遊戲》之前構思的《[[死者代言人|死者代言人]]》（1986年），和《{{link-en|屠異|Xenocide}}》（1991年）、《{{link-en|意念之子|Children of the Mind}}》（1996年）和《{{link-en|安德的流亡|Ender in Exile}}》（2008年），講述安德在後續旅程中到達銀河裡各個不同世界的故事。其中，《安德的流亡》部分銜接了《戰爭遊戲》末尾的劇情<ref name="Deseret News"/>。此外，卡德也出版了背景設定與《戰爭遊戲》同步的平行中篇小說《{{link-en|安德的影子|Ender's Shadow}}》（1996年）和《{{link-en|安德的禮物|A War of Gifts: An Ender Story}}》（2007年），兩者採用不同的角色來敘事，前者是安德的天才隊友豆子<ref name="Salon"/>，後者則是戰鬥學校的另一個學生塞克·摩根（{{lang|en|Zeck Morgan}}，並未出現在《戰爭遊戲》中）<ref name="SFR-Gifts">{{cite web |last=Wagner |first=Thomas M. |url=http://sfreviews.net/osc_war_of_gifts.html |title=A WAR OF GIFTS (2007) |work=SFReviews.net |date=2007 |accessdate=2019-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180410181714/http://sfreviews.net/osc_war_of_gifts.html |archive-date=2018-04-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="SFS-Gifts">{{cite web |last=Silver |first=Steven H |url=https://www.sfsite.com/02b/wg266.htm |title=A War of Gifts |work=SF Site |date=2008 |accessdate=2019-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160412091134/https://www.sfsite.com/02b/wg266.htm |archive-date=2016-04-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2013年，在接受《{{link-en|猶他新聞|Deseret News}}》{{refnest|name="猶他新聞"|group="備註"}}採訪時，卡德表示，「多年來我一直在調整《戰爭遊戲》的故事，第一次是將短篇小說發展成長篇小說，第二次是《安德的影子》，再來就是《安德的流亡》」<ref name="Deseret News"/>。

== 改編作品 ==

=== 電影 ===
[[File:Gavin_Hood_2015.jpg|thumb]]<small>（2015年）</small>]]

{{Main|安德的游戏 (电影)}}

《戰爭遊戲》於1985年出版後，許多好萊塢的片商前來叩關，但卡德始終不答應<ref>{{cite news | last = Lozano | first = Alicia | url = http://articles.latimes.com/2009/jan/05/entertainment/et-card5 | title = Orson Scott Card and his world of Ender | work = ''[[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]]'' | date = 2009-01-05 | accessdate = 2009-03-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090330131424/http://articles.latimes.com/2009/jan/05/entertainment/et-card5 | archive-date = 2009-03-30 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。1996年之後，卡德決定自行創作劇本<ref>{{cite news | last = Paul | first = Cannon | title = The Game Is Afoot | url = http://movies.ign.com/articles/359/359290p1.html | work = ''[[IGN|IGN]]'' | date = 2002-05-13 | accessdate = 2009-03-11 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120726140031/http://movies.ign.com/articles/359/359290p1.html | archive-date = 2012-07-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，前後一共進行了六次左右<ref name="Wired"/>。卡德在受訪時表示，《戰爭遊戲》是不適合搬上大螢幕的，因為有很多安德的內心戲，而且對於那些沒讀過原著的人而言不太好懂<ref name="Wired"/>。2009年2月，卡德表示，他已經為製片公司{{link-en|MWM Studios|MWM Studios|OddLot Entertainment}}（現名MWM Studios）完成了一份劇本<ref name="Taleswapper, Inc">{{cite web|url=http://www.taleswapper.net/movies/endersgame/endersgame_update.html|title=Movie production team being assembled|date=2009-02-25|publisher=Taleswapper, Inc|accessdate=2009-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090220125031/http://www.taleswapper.net/movies/endersgame/endersgame_update.html|archive-date=2009-02-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隔年9月，[[加文·胡德|加文·胡德]]簽約執導電影版<ref name="Zeitchik">{{cite news|last=Zeitchik|first=Steven|title=Gavin Hood looks to play 'Ender's Game'|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2010/09/orson-scott-card-enders-game-gavin-hood.html|newspaper=''Los Angeles Times''|date=2010-09-20|access-date=2019-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190107185525/https://latimesblogs.latimes.com/movies/2010/09/orson-scott-card-enders-game-gavin-hood.html|archive-date=2019-01-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年4月，據報導，[[頂峰娛樂|頂峰娛樂]]將資助該片的製作，並擔任發行商<ref>{{cite news|last=Gallagher|first=Brian|title=Ender's Game Lands at Summit Entertainment|url=http://www.movieweb.com/news/enders-game-lands-at-summit-entertainment|work=MovieWeb|access-date=2019-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016003927/http://www.movieweb.com/news/enders-game-lands-at-summit-entertainment|archive-date=2013-10-16|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=McNary|first=Dave|title=Summit plays 'Ender's Game'|url=http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118036112|newspaper=Variety|date=2011-04-28|access-date=2019-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120229162812/http://www.variety.com/article/VR1118036112|archive-date=2012-02-29|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年年底，兩位主角安德和格拉夫上校的演員敲定，分別是[[阿萨·巴特菲尔德|阿萨·巴特菲尔德]]<ref name="asacast">{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2011/film/news/asa-butterfield-locks-ender-s-game-1118046778/|work=''Variety''|first=Jeff|last=Sneider|title=Asa Butterfield locks 'Ender's Game'|date=2011-11-29|access-date=2019-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190607042254/https://variety.com/2011/film/news/asa-butterfield-locks-ender-s-game-1118046778/|archive-date=2019-06-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[哈里森·福特|哈里森·福特]]<ref name="Variety2011">{{cite journal |url=https://variety.com/2011/film/news/harrison-ford-locked-for-ender-s-game-1118047827/ |title=Harrison Ford locked for ''Ender's Game'': OddLot's sci-fi tentpole gains trio of Oscar nominees |last=Sneider |first=Jeff |work=''Variety'' |date=2011-12-21 |journal= |author= |access-date=2019-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190607042339/https://variety.com/2011/film/news/harrison-ford-locked-for-ender-s-game-1118047827/ |archive-date=2019-06-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。卡德本人出任該片的製片人<ref>{{cite news |last=Sneider |first=Jeff |title=Asa Butterfield locks 'Ender's Game' |url=http://variety.com/2011/film/news/asa-butterfield-locks-ender-s-game-1118046778/ |work=''Variety'' |date=2011-11-29 |access-date=2019-07-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190607042254/https://variety.com/2011/film/news/asa-butterfield-locks-ender-s-game-1118046778/ |archive-date=2019-06-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，同時也在片中以聲音客串<ref name="AICN">{{cite web|url=http://www.aintitcool.com/node/55810|title=So Orson Scott Card Visited The Set Of The ENDER'S GAME Movie...|last=Oliver|first=Glen "Merrick"|date=2012-05-17|work={{link-en|Ain't It Cool News|Ain't It Cool News}}|accessdate=2012-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120520024613/http://www.aintitcool.com/node/55810|archive-date=2012-05-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影於2012年2月底在美國的[[新奥尔良|新奥尔良]]開拍<ref>{{cite web |author=Christine |url=http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2012/03/01/enders-game-begins-filming-at-the-michoud-assembly-facility-in-new-orleans/ |title='Ender's Game' begins filming at the Michoud Assembly Facility in New Orleans |publisher=''On Location Vacations'' |date=2012-03-01 |accessdate=2013-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130526143045/http://www.onlocationvacations.com/2012/03/01/enders-game-begins-filming-at-the-michoud-assembly-facility-in-new-orleans/ |archive-date=2013-05-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並於2013年11月1日在美國院線上映<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.comingsoon.net/films.php?id=69977 |title=Ender's Game Trailer, News, Videos, and Reviews |publisher=ComingSoon.net |date= |accessdate=2013-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130323032945/http://www.comingsoon.net/films.php?id=69977 |archive-date=2013-03-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，影評人對該片的評價整體而言褒貶不一<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/enders-game/|title=Ender's Game (2013)|work=[[爛番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]]|publisher=Fandango Media|accessdate=2019-05-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141116084905/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/enders-game/|archive-date=2014-11-16|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.metacritic.com/movie/enders-game |title= Ender's Game Reviews |publisher= [[CBS互動|CBS Interactive]] |work= [[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate= 2019-05-19 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20141116085028/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/enders-game |archive-date= 2014-11-16 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。該片的全球票房僅1.25億美元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=endersgame.htm |title=Ender's Game |website=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |accessdate=2014-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140404143856/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=endersgame.htm |archive-date=2014-04-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，對比其高額成本，《[[綜藝_(雜誌)|綜藝]]》雜誌將該片列為「2013年好萊塢最大的[[票房炸弹|票房炸弹]]」<ref>{{cite news |last=Variety Staff |date=2013-12-26 |title=Hollywood’s Biggest Box Office Bombs of 2013 |url=https://variety.com/gallery/box-office-disappointments-of-2013/#!2/enders-game/ |newspaper=''Variety'' |accessdate=2014-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231000226/http://variety.com/gallery/box-office-disappointments-of-2013/#!2/enders-game/ |archive-date=2013-12-31 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 電子遊戲 ===

2008年，據報導，《戰爭遊戲》的電子遊戲正在製作當中<ref>{{cite web |last=Kietzmann |first=Ludwig |url=https://www.engadget.com/2008/01/29/undertow-team-creating-orson-scott-cards-enders-games-game/ |title=Undertow team creating Orson Scott Card's Ender's Game's game |work=[[Engadget|Engadget]] |date=2008-01-29 |accessdate=2019-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180226032713/https://www.engadget.com/2008/01/29/undertow-team-creating-orson-scott-cards-enders-games-game/ |archive-date=2018-02-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，標題為《戰爭遊戲：戰鬥室》（{{lang|en|''Ender's Game: Battle Room''}}），預計以數位形式發行，可在任何提供下載功能的平台遊玩<ref name="Newsweek-Game">{{cite magazine|url=http://blog.newsweek.com/blogs/levelup/archive/2008/01/29/exclusive-donald-and-geremy-mustard-discuss-plans-for-ender-s-game.aspx|title=Exclusive: Chair Entertainment's Donald and Geremy Mustard Shed Some Light On Their Plans For 'Ender's Game'|accessdate=2009-01-05|magazine=''[[新闻周刊|Newsweek]]''|date=2008-01-29|last=Croal|first=N'Gai|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080603193919/http://blog.newsweek.com/blogs/levelup/archive/2008/01/29/exclusive-donald-and-geremy-mustard-discuss-plans-for-ender-s-game.aspx|archivedate=2008-06-03|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。遊戲由曾製作[[Xbox_Live_Arcade|Xbox Live Arcade]]遊戲《{{link-en|Undertow (遊戲)|Undertow (video game)|Undertow}}》和《{{link-en|闇影帝國|Shadow Complex}}》的[[Chair_Entertainment|Chair Entertainment]]開發。官方透露的遊戲訊息很少，只有提到這款遊戲設定在「{{link-en|安德的遊戲 (系列)|Ender's Game (series)|安德宇宙}}」中，並且會以原著中用來模擬戰鬥的「戰鬥室」為重點。<ref name="Newsweek-Game"/>2010年12月，據報導，《戰爭遊戲：戰鬥室》的開發作業已經中止，整個計劃被無限期擱置<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.joystiq.com/2010/12/14/enders-game-tabled-by-chair|title=Ender's Game tabled by Chair|accessdate=2012-03-29|publisher=''[[Joystiq|Joystiq]]''|date=2010-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018191438/http://www.joystiq.com/2010/12/14/enders-game-tabled-by-chair/|archive-date=2012-10-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。卡德也曾與Amaze Entertainment簽過有關《戰爭遊戲》改編電子遊戲的合約，但最後並沒有付諸實現<ref>{{cite interview|interviewer=Kevin Savetz|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mWFZ84u11Wo|title=Orson Scott Card interview — Atari computers & computer games|accessdate=2019-07-28|publisher=[[YouTube|YouTube]]|date=2018-01-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180704134700/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mWFZ84u11Wo|archivedate=2018-07-04|deadurl=no}}</ref>。

=== 漫畫 ===
{{main|{{link-en|戰爭遊戲 (漫畫)|Ender's Game (comics)}}}}

2008年4月19日，[[漫威漫畫|漫威漫畫]]與卡德宣布，他們將出版《戰爭遊戲》的改編{{link-en|限量系列|Limited series (comics)}}漫畫，且未來其他的《戰爭遊戲》系列作品也會全部改編成漫畫。卡德表示，此舉是讓《戰爭遊戲》不再只是文字，且讀者能看見畫面的第一步。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.marvel.com/news/comicstories.3185.NYCC_~apos~08~colon~_Ender~apos~s_Game_Coming_to_Marvel|title=NYCC '08: Marvel to Adapt Orson Scott Card's Ender's Game Series|last=Penagos|first=Ryan|date=2008-05-12|publisher=Marvel Characters, Inc.|accessdate=2008-09-13|archive-url=https://archive.is/20120630010810/http://www.marvel.com/news/comicstories.3185.NYCC_~apos~08~colon~_Ender~apos~s_Game_Coming_to_Marvel|archive-date=2012-06-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2008年年底，首兩套漫畫正式出版，第一套漫畫共有五期，名為《戰爭遊戲：戰鬥學校》（{{lang|en|''Ender's Game: Battle School''}}），由{{link-en|克里斯多夫·尤斯特|Christopher Yost}}創作<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.marvel.com/comics/issue/22362/enders_game_2008_1|publisher=Marvel.com|title=Ender's Game (2008) #1|accessdate=2019-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190730015504/https://www.marvel.com/comics/issue/22362/enders_game_2008_1|archive-date=2019-07-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而第二套漫畫也有五期，名為《-{zh-cn:安德的影子;zh-tw:安德闇影;}-：戰鬥學校》（{{lang|en|''Ender's Shadow: Battle School''}}），由{{link-en|麥克·凱利 (作家)|Mike Carey (writer)|麥克·凱利}}創作<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.tfaw.com/Profile/Enders-Shadow-Battle-School-1-%28of-5%29___333429|date=1986–2009|publisher=Things From Another World, Inc.|title=Enders Shadow Battle School #1 (of 5)|accessdate=2009-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081224083006/http://www.tfaw.com/Profile/Enders-Shadow-Battle-School-1-%28of-5%29___333429|archive-date=2008-12-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。後續漫畫陸陸續續地出版，最新的一套於2012年出版<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.marvel.com/comics/series/7805/formic_wars_silent_strike_2011_-_2012|publisher=Marvel.com|title=Formic Wars: Silent Strike (2011 - 2012)|accessdate=2019-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190730015501/https://www.marvel.com/comics/series/7805/formic_wars_silent_strike_2011_-_2012|archive-date=2019-07-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 廣播劇 ===

卡德後來將《戰爭遊戲》改編成[[廣播劇|廣播劇]]《戰爭遊戲不死：全角色廣播劇》（{{lang|en|''Ender's Game Alive: The Full Cast Audioplay''}}），於2013年由{{link-en|Audible (商店)|Audible (store)|Audible.com}}推出<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/18715259-ender-s-game-alive|publisher=[[Goodreads|Goodreads]]|title=Ender's Game Alive: The Full Cast Audioplay|accessdate=2019-07-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190508045843/https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/18715259-ender-s-game-alive|archive-date=2019-05-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該劇共動用了30名配音員，來為100多個角色配音<ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://skyboatmedia.com/enders-game-alive/ |title=Ender'S Game Alive – The Full Cast Audioplay By Orson Scott Card |publisher=Skyboat Media |date=2013-10-01 |accessdate=2013-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131101213951/http://skyboatmedia.com/enders-game-alive/ |archive-date=2013-11-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=from Skyboat Media Plus 3 weeks ago not yet rated |url=http://vimeo.com/76188947 |title=Orson Scott Card – Author of Ender's Game Alive on Vimeo |publisher=Vimeo.com |date=2013-10-04 |accessdate=2013-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131023005508/http://vimeo.com/76188947 |archive-date=2013-10-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 影響 ==

在{{link-en|恩斯特·克萊恩|Ernest Cline}}創作的2015年科幻小說《{{link-en|一級艦隊|Armada (novel)}}》中，《戰爭遊戲》扮演著重要的角色<ref>{{Harvnb|恩斯特·克萊恩|2018|p=5}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Hudson |first=Laura |url=https://slate.com/culture/2015/07/armada-by-ernest-cline-follow-up-to-ready-player-one-reviewed.html |title=Serious Bill-Paying Skillage |work=''Slate'' |date=2015-07-07 |accessdate=2019-08-03 |archive-date=2021-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226203625/https://slate.com/culture/2015/07/armada-by-ernest-cline-follow-up-to-ready-player-one-reviewed.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/arts/books-and-media/book-reviews/review-in-ernest-clines-armada-geek-culture-dies-in-the-vacuum-of-space/article25876689/ |title=Review: In Ernest Cline’s Armada, geek culture dies in the vacuum of space |work=''The Globe and Mail'' |date=2015-08-07 |accessdate=2019-08-03 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124212829/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/arts/books-and-media/book-reviews/review-in-ernest-clines-armada-geek-culture-dies-in-the-vacuum-of-space/article25876689/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

